    "when using an optimization algorithm with a line search and a convergence criterion, we can predict locally optimal solutions.",
    "There are many times when we can take the local optimal solution as the resulting exact solution, but there are also times when the local optimal solution we obtain may be highly biased.",
    "In order to avoid large deviations in the solution, we propose a reactivation technique for reactivating the optimization algorithm to go back to the optimal solution.",
    "The core idea of the algorithm is to suitably loosen the line search condition of the optimization algorithm after its convergence.",
    "The PINNs in this paper use an Adma optimizer that includes strong Wolfe."
